title: Welcome
section: HADC! is the Harper Adams Data Club
text:
HADC! is the Harper Adams Data Club
This site is devoted to the R programming, Statistics and Data Science community at Harper Adams University. Our meetings are a mix of live coding, tutorials, and group problem solving. We are a friendly and enthusiastic group of students and staff from a variety of disciplines.

We meet weekly, currently on Tuesdays at 4pm UK time on Teams
Join our Discord server (please join with your full real name, e.g. “Florence Nightingale”).
 Youtube channel TheStatisticsLab
